    public class LazyCANTalon
extends com.ctre.phoenix.motorcontrol.can.WPI_TalonSRX
    This class is a thin wrapper around the CANTalon that reduces CAN bus / CPU overhead by skipping duplicate set commands. (By default the Talon flushes the Tx buffer on every set call).
